query:
SELECT 
  qp.questionId,
  qp.firstAttemptStatus,
  'ORPHANED - Question deleted' as status
FROM question_progress qp
LEFT JOIN questions q ON qp.questionId = q.id
WHERE qp.userId = (SELECT id FROM users WHERE email = 'testyou@me.com')
  AND q.id IS NULL;
